        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Loan of $500.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>New Orleans</placeName>, <date when="1821-11-20">Novr. 20. 1821</date></p>
<p>One hundred Twenty days after date (this my only exchange same
tenor and date) pay <persName>Mr Stephen F Austin</persName> or order Five Hundred
Dollars value received and charge the same to</p>
<p>Yr Obt Servt</p>

<p><persName>Edward Lovelace</persName></p>
<p><persName>Messrs. Reynolds and Ralston <placeName>New Orleans</placeName></persName></p>

<p>[ Endorsed: ]</p>

<p>Amt____________________________________________________________   $500

2 1/2 % per acceptg____________________________________________     12. 50
											________
											 512. 50</p>
<p>Recd Pay of the above Amt say Five Hundred &amp; Twelve 50/100 Dolls</p>

<p><persName>Reynolds &amp; Ralston</persName></p>
<p><persName>Hugh Bell</persName></p>
<p><placeName>N. O.</placeName> <date when="1822-03-30">30th March 1822</date></p>

        </div1>
